Story E2-S1 ‚Äì Highlight Period Days
As a user, I want to see my period days highlighted on the calendar so that I can easily understand my cycle history.

Story Points: 3

Acceptance Criteria:

All logged period dates are highlighted (for example with a colored marker).

Past cycles remain visible when navigating to older months.

Highlights do not conflict with predicted dates or today‚Äôs marker.

Story E2-S2 ‚Äì Navigate Months
As a user, I want to move to previous and next months so that I can review past and future dates.

Story Points: 1

Acceptance Criteria:

User can move to previous and next months using arrows or swipe.

