Highlights remain correct after navigation.

Story E2-S3 ‚Äì Tap to Select Date
As a user, I want to tap a date on the calendar so that I can quickly log or edit my period.

Story Points: 2

Acceptance Criteria:

Tapping a date marks it as ‚Äúselected‚Äù.

