As a user, I want to know if my cycles are regular or irregular so that I can understand my health better.

Story Points: 3

Acceptance Criteria:

App calculates variation in cycle length.

Uses a simple rule (e.g. variation less than ~3 days = regular).

Shows a label like ‚ÄúRegular‚Äù or ‚ÄúIrregular‚Äù with green/orange colour.

